# Typography

## Font Family
Only Inter: `'Inter_Subset', 'Inter', sans-serif`

## Scale (use explicit px in Tailwind)
- Caption: `text-[10px]` uppercase, medium weight
- XS: `text-[12px]` — labels, hyperlinks, descriptions
- SM: `text-[14px]` — default UI text, buttons, filters
- Base: `text-[16px]` — table data
- LG: `text-[18px]` — card titles
- XL: `text-[24px]`
- 2XL: `text-[36px]`
- Page title: `text-[32px] font-semibold`
- Section title: `text-[20px] font-medium`

## Weights
- Regular: 400, Medium: 500, Semibold: 600, Bold: 700

## Rules
- DO NOT use Tailwind text size classes (text-lg, text-xl) for body text
- DO NOT use Tailwind font weight classes (font-bold) unless requested
- Use explicit pixel values: `text-[14px]`, `text-[12px]`
- Line height: 1.5 for readability
